Notifications on the transport tax will stop sending by mail - website Behind the wheel www.zr.ru
The Tax Inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notifications of property taxes.
All Russian car owners have become accustomed to the unchanged scheme: in summer and autumn they receive by mail a receipt for the payment of a transport tax for the previous year.
However, many of them will not wait this year.
The fact is that the tax inspection without excessive noise has changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal Cabinet of the taxpayer" on the official website of the ministry nalog.ru, notifications will come in electronic form.
In the inspection, such Russians were automatically considered online users and removed them from the standard, "paper" mailing.
The news will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
All the others will still receive the usual letters.
However, the opportunity to return to the old scheme is also available to account holders on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax department during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and convenient.
The notification will appear in the "Personal Cabinet" immediately after drafting, while the letter will go a few days and may be lost altogether.
In addition, the number of users of the online service of the tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to save seriously on the mail.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection site is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in a “personal office” to get a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without knowing it themselves, will fall into the category of non-payers with all the resulting consequences.
Access to the "Personal office of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, by means of an electronic signature or by entering the login and password indicated in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained in person at any tax inspection office (regardless of the place of registration on the account).
We would like to remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid by December 1.
Notifications were sent in July.
